1 b. Once the bureau, after consultation with the state court administrator, determines
2 and implements an electronic method to notify law enforcement about the order,
3 the clerk of court's requirement to forward the order to the law enforcement
4 agency will be satisfied.
5 c. Once the bureau, after consultation with the director of state radio, determines
